      "what_this_shows": "The naive agent always routes to billing_team. When the email thread shifts topic (billing -> legal, with injection), the wrong routing at step N triggers the cascade: an escalation email from the sender's lawyer appears at step N+2. This is a direct consequence of the agent's earlier decision — exactly the delayed-consequence property that defines RL environments.",
